description:
Fear is not real.
The only place that fear can exist is in out thoughts of the future. It is a product of our imagination causing us to fear things that do not exist. That is near insanity. Do not misunderstand me... Danger is very real... But fear? That is a choice ... 2020 is a year full of choices. Choose wisely ... but don’t forget fear doesn’t stop death, it stops life✌️#thetruthisoutthere
